short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension provides navigation history for tabs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Use keyboard shortcuts to navigate to previously visited Chrome tabs. 
No more endless clicking or scrolling through your browser history! 

Benefits for multi-tab users:

* Boost productivity: Quickly switch between your last visited tabs, keeping your workflow smooth and efficient.
* Instant access: Jump back to recently viewed tabs without losing your context.
* Streamlined navigation: Effortlessly retrace your steps and find the information you need.
* Enhanced focus: Stay organized and on track, even with dozens of tabs open.

Ideal for:

 - Researchers
 - Developers
 - Students
 - Writers
 - Anyone who works with multiple tabs simultaneously

Take control of your browsing history and reclaim valuable time with Tab Back!

The following keyboard shortcuts are available:

Back: Ctrl + Shift + K Go to the previous tab in history
Forward: Ctrl + Shift + L Go to the next tab in history
Toggle: Ctrl + Shift + P Toggle between the current and previously visited tab

Note: Control key is used on both PC and Mac computers.
